---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="MinimalDev — Free Online Utility Tools"
  description="Free online calculators, converters, and utility tools for everyday tasks. Simple, fast, and mobile-friendly."
  canonicalPath="/"
>
  <div class="container">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="card" style="padding:18px;">
      <div style="display:flex; gap:14px; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <div style="min-width:240px; max-width:720px;">
          <h1 class="page-title" style="margin:0 0 8px;">
            Free Online Tools & Practical Guides
          </h1>

          <p class="lead" style="margin:0 0 8px;">
            MinimalDev provides simple online calculators, converters, and clear guides for everyday tasks.
          </p>

          <p class="lead" style="margin:0;">
            Understand when to use each tool and get accurate results quickly.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-top:14px;">
        <a class="btn" href="/math/">Start with Math</a>
        <a class="btn secondary" href="/converter/">Browse Converters</a>
        <a class="btn secondary" href="/categories/">All Categories</a>
        <a class="btn secondary" href="/guides/">Guides</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Guides & Practical Tips</h2>
      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:0;">
        Read practical explanations before using tools. These guides explain formats, calculations, conversions, and real-world use cases so you can choose the right tool and understand the result.
      </p>

      <div class="grid">
        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Image Guide</span>
          <h2>Image Format Comparison</h2>
          <p>Compare PNG, JPG, and WebP, including when each format is best for photos, graphics, transparency, and web performance.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/image-format-comparison/">Read Guide</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Image Guide</span>
          <h2>Reduce Image Size</h2>
          <p>Learn how compression affects file size and quality, and when JPG or WebP compression is the better choice.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/reduce-image-size/">Read Guide</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Image Guide</span>
          <h2>Why Use WebP</h2>
          <p>Understand why WebP can improve page speed, how it compares with JPG and PNG, and when it is worth using.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/why-use-webp/">Read Guide</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Image Guide</span>
          <h2>JPG vs PNG</h2>
          <p>Learn the practical difference between JPG and PNG for photos, screenshots, logos, transparency, and sharp graphics.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/jpg-vs-png/">Read Guide</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Image Guide</span>
          <h2>Image Resize Guide</h2>
          <p>Resize images while preserving aspect ratio, avoiding distortion, and choosing suitable dimensions for web or social use.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/image-resize-guide/">Read Guide</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Performance Guide</span>
          <h2>Image Optimization for Web</h2>
          <p>Learn how optimized images improve loading speed, reduce bandwidth, and create a better website experience.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/image-optimization-for-web/">Read Guide</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Developer Guide</span>
          <h2>JSON Formatting Basics</h2>
          <p>Understand why formatting, validating, and minifying JSON matters when working with APIs and configuration data.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/json-formatting-basics/">Read Guide</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Finance Guide</span>
          <h2>Loan and Interest Basics</h2>
          <p>Learn how monthly payments, total interest, and amortization affect the real cost of borrowing money.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/guides/loan-interest-basics/">Read Guide</a>
        </section>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Why Use MinimalDev Tools?</h2>

      <div class="card" style="padding:18px;">
        <div class="prose">

          <p>
            MinimalDev provides practical online tools designed for real-world use cases.
            Each tool focuses on solving a specific problem quickly, without unnecessary complexity.
          </p>

          <p>
            Unlike many generic tool websites, this platform emphasizes clarity and accuracy.
            Tools include detailed explanations, real examples, and guidance to help users understand results, not just generate them.
          </p>

          <h3>What You Can Do Here</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Calculate financial values such as loans and compound interest</li>
            <li>Format and validate developer data like JSON and Base64</li>
            <li>Generate secure random strings and identifiers</li>
            <li>Convert units and measurements accurately</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Designed for Practical Use</h3>
          <p>
            All tools run directly in your browser with no data sent to servers.
            This ensures privacy, speed, and reliability for everyday tasks.
          </p>

          <p>
            Whether you are a developer, student, or general user, MinimalDev helps you get accurate results with clear understanding.
          </p>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- POPULAR TOOLS (기존 6개 유지) -->
    <section class="section">
      <h2>Popular tools</h2>
      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:0;">
        Start with commonly used tools for calculations, conversions, and quick checks.
      </p>

      <div class="grid">

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Math</span>
          <h2>Percent Calculator</h2>
          <p>Calculate percentages and changes.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/math/percent-calculator/">Open</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Finance</span>
          <h2>Compound Interest Calculator</h2>
          <p>Calculate long-term investment growth with compounding.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/finance/compound-interest-calculator/">Open</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Finance</span>
          <h2>Loan Calculator</h2>
          <p>Estimate loan payments and total interest.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/finance/loan-calculator/">Open</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Utility</span>
          <h2>JSON Formatter</h2>
          <p>Format, validate, and debug JSON data easily.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/utility/json-formatter/">Open</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Utility</span>
          <h2>Base64 Encoder & Decoder</h2>
          <p>Encode and decode Base64 securely in your browser.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/utility/base64/">Open</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <span class="badge">Utility</span>
          <h2>Random String Generator</h2>
          <p>Generate secure random strings for tokens and IDs.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/utility/random-string-generator/">Open</a>
        </section>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CATEGORY (기존 6개 유지) -->
    <section class="section">
      <h2>Browse by category</h2>
      <p class="lead" style="margin-top:0;">
        Explore tools by category to quickly find what you need.
      </p>

      <div class="grid">
        <section class="card">
          <h2>Converters</h2>
          <p>Unit conversion tools.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/converter/">Open</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <h2>Math</h2>
          <p>Calculation tools.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/math/">Open</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <h2>Finance</h2>
          <p>Financial calculators.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/finance/">Open</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <h2>Date-Time</h2>
          <p>Date and time tools.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/date-time/">Open</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <h2>Health</h2>
          <p>Health-related calculators.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/health/">Open</a>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
          <h2>All Categories</h2>
          <p>Browse all tools.</p>
          <a class="btn" href="/categories/">Open</a>
        </section>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About -->
    <section class="section">
      <h2>About MinimalDev</h2>
      <div class="card" style="padding:18px;">
        <p style="margin-top:0;">
          MinimalDev focuses on simple tools with clear explanations.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-bottom:0;">
          Each tool solves one problem clearly and efficiently.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>